  "texts": [
    "All interviews were held in English and audio-recorded using Zoom but stored locally.",
    "The audio recordings were transcribed verbatim.",
    "Data analysisWe opted to use reflexive thematic analysis (TA) as our analytical framework, enabling us to contextualize our analysis for healthcare and uncover intricate and underlying patterns of meaning within the available data [26].",
    "In particular, we chose reflexive TA because this study aimed at a deep and nuanced understanding of the data that captures the complexities of developing AI for healthcare without rigid preconceptions [27].",
    "Two authors (L.A.O, M.R.)"
  ]
